Package org.ginsim.core.graph

Class AbstractGraph<V,​E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.core.graph.AbstractGraph<V,​E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of vertices
    E - the type of edges
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph<V,​E>, GraphModel<V,​E>, GraphViewListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractDerivedGraph, RegulatoryGraphImpl, TreeImpl
    public abstract class AbstractGraph<V,​E extends Edge<V>>
extends Object
implements Graph<V,​E>, GraphViewListener
    Base class for graphs using a storage backend: it provides generic methods and storage abstraction. The actual structure is stored in the graph backend, and classes deriving from this one can provide specialised methods.
    Author:
    Lionel Spinelli, Aurelien Naldi
